# Title: Activate Suppression of Windows Security Center Notifications
# Author: frack113
# Date: 2022-08-19
# Level: medium
# Description: Detect set Notification_Suppress to 1 to disable the Windows security center notification
# MITRE Tactic: Persistence
# Tags: attack.persistence, attack.defense-impairment, attack.t1112
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/windows/registry/registry_set/registry_set_suppress_defender_notifications.yml

Details="DWORD (0x00000001)" TargetObject="*SOFTWARE\\Policies\\Microsoft\\Windows Defender\\UX Configuration\\Notification_Suppress"